  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>A breakfast buffet is served every morning with continental and hot cooked options. Dinner is a four course meal including a buffet of starters and salad. Once a week the hotel arrange a <span>Trentino dinner where you can sample some great local cuisine.</span></p>
<p>The restaurant here serves up traditional Ladin dishes as well as national and international cuisine. It's all made with fresh produce and you can expect <span>hearty and delicious mountain food. </span>They have a wine cellar too with a large selection of traditional Trentino wines.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
