  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Standard Rooms</strong> are around 20m² and sleep up to four people (extra beds are either a single or double sofa bed). The spacious rooms are finished in a modern alpine style and have a balcony.</p>
<p><strong>Single Rooms</strong> are around 18m². They do not have a balcony.</p>
<p><strong>All rooms have:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Shower</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
<li>TV</li>
<li>Safe</li>
</ul>
<p>Cots are available for €20 euro per day, payable locally. </p>
<p><strong>Local fees &amp; taxes</strong></p>
<p>A resort tax of approx. €2.50 per person per day is payable locally.</p>
<p><strong>Accessibility</strong></p>]]></roomsDescription>
